media-mp4-codec - MP4 Codec Conversion

USAGE:
    media-mp4-codec

DESCRIPTION:
    Convert MP4 files to supported codecs. Converts non-H264/HEVC
    files to the configured codec to ensure compatibility.

SUPPORTED CODECS:
    - h264 (H.264)
    - hevc (H.265)

UNSUPPORTED:
    - mpeg4 (does not work)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-media-management-video-codec CODEC
        Target video codec (default: h264)

    -conf-media-management-video-codec-tag TAG
        Video codec tag

EXAMPLES:
    media-mp4-codec
